description: "What's My Sign" is a daily horoscope.  Based on your astrological sign, it will provide you with your daily motivation based on your stars.  Just say, "Alexa, ask whats my sign".  And then say your astrological sign.  The following signs will work:  Aquarius, Pisces, Aries, Taurus, Gemini, Cancer, Leo, Virgo, Libra, Scorpio, Sagittarius, and Capricorn.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask what's my sign for Sagittarius
Alexa, ask what's my sign for Taurus
Alexa, ask what's my sign for Cancer
name: What's My Sign
